Package: libopencog-agents
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         libatomspace (>= 5.0.5),
         libcogutil (>= 1.0.0)
Description: OpenCog agents library (runtime)
 The Agents module provides interactive agent capabilities for the
 OpenCog cognitive architecture, enabling autonomous reasoning and
 action execution.
 .
 This package contains the shared libraries for runtime use.

